  "response": "Quora was co-founded by Adam D'Angelo and Charlie Cheever in June 2009. Adam D'Angelo, who previously served as the CTO of Facebook, was the driving force behind the platform's development, while Charlie Cheever also had a background at Facebook. The site was designed to be a question-and-answer platform where users can ask questions and receive answers from other users, leveraging collective knowledge and expertise.",
